## 📺 画面表示用コード

```typescript
// 除算演算子
let a: number = 20;
let b: number = 4;
let quotient: number = a / b; // 5

// 実用的な例
let totalAmount: number = 1200;
let people: number = 4;
let perPerson: number = totalAmount / people; // 300

let price: number = 1000;
let discountRate: number = 0.2;
let discountAmount: number = price * discountRate; // 200
```

